text: Karma Rangdol is a Bhutanese politician who has been a Bhutan Peace and Prosperity Party (DPT) member of the National Assembly of Bhutan from 2013 to 2018. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Bhutanese MNAs 2013–2018 Category:21st-century politicians Category:Druk Phuensum Tshogpa politicians Category:Bhutanese politicians Category:Druk Phuensum Tshogpa MNAs
